Package: multiomfigR
Title: NC-Style Multi-Omics Integration Figure Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Jiang", family = "Congxin", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jcx981212@163.com")
Author: Jiang Congxin
Maintainer: Jiang Congxin <jcx981212@163.com>
Description: R toolkit for training and generating NC-style multi-omics integration figures from traceable embedding, modality metric, cross-dataset validation, regulatory link, and pathway program source-data tables. It builds on ncfigR for shared theme, heatmap, network, embedding, composition, and export conventions.
